            S0/0/1              192.168.5.2        255.255.255.0          N/A

R3          G0/1                192.168.3.1        255.255.255.0          N/A
            S0/0/0              192.168.4.1        255.255.255.0          N/A
            S0/0/1              192.168.5.1        255.255.255.0          N/A

